#つぶやきProcessing
t=0
draw=_=>{t||createCanvas(W=600,W,WEBGL)
rotateY(t+=.01)
background(0)
for(x=9;x--;)for(y=9;y--;)for(z=9;z--;)x&7&&y&7&&z&7||(X=x-4,Y=y-4,Z=z-4,l=map(cos(t*2),-.3,.3,30,170/dist(X,Y,Z,0,0,0),1),stroke((x+9)*16,(y+9)*16,(z+9)*16),point(X*l,Y*l+9,Z*l))} https://t.co/sfwbCztC2O
